properties.name: AnimationEaseMode
properties.description: Specifies the animation easing mode.

properties.name: AnnotationType
properties.description: Specifies whether the annotation displays text, an image, or a template.

properties.name: ArgumentAxisHoverMode
properties.description: Specifies chart elements to be highlighted when a user points to an axis label.

properties.name: AxisScaleType
properties.description: Specifies the type of the axis.

subMembers.name: BaseChartAdaptiveLayout
subMembers.description: Specifies adaptive layout properties.

subMembers.name: height
subMembers.description: Specifies the minimum container height at which the layout begins to adapt.

subMembers.name: keepLabels
subMembers.description: Specifies whether [point labels] should be kept when the UI component adapts the layout.

subMembers.name: width
subMembers.description: Specifies the minimum container width at which the layout begins to adapt.

subMembers.name: BaseChartLegend
subMembers.description: Specifies properties of the legend.

subMembers.name: customizeItems
subMembers.description: Allows you to change the order, text, and visibility of legend items.

subMembers.name: markerTemplate
subMembers.description: Specifies an SVG element that serves as a custom legend item marker.

subMembers.name: BaseChartTooltip
subMembers.description: Configures tooltips.

subMembers.name: argumentFormat
subMembers.description: Formats the point argument before it is displayed in the tooltip. To format the point value, use the [format] property.

subMembers.name: contentTemplate
subMembers.description: Specifies a custom template for a tooltip.

subMembers.name: customizeTooltip
subMembers.description: Allows you to change tooltip appearance.

subMembers.name: interactive
subMembers.description: Allows users to interact with the tooltip content.

subMembers.name: shared
subMembers.description: Specifies whether the tooltip is shared across all series points with the same argument.

properties.name: ChartsAxisLabelOverlap
properties.description: Decides how to arrange axis labels when there is not enough space to display all of them.

subMembers.name: ChartsColor
subMembers.description: Specifies the chart's color.

subMembers.name: base
subMembers.description: Specifies the base color for series, points and labels.

subMembers.name: fillId
subMembers.description: Specifies the id of the gradient or pattern.

properties.name: ChartsDataType
properties.description: Specifies the type of axis values.

properties.name: ChartsLabelOverlap
properties.description: Specifies how the chart must behave when [series point labels] overlap.

properties.name: DashStyle
properties.description: Sets a dash style for the chart elements.

properties.name: DiscreteAxisDivisionMode
properties.description: Specifies whether ticks/grid lines of a discrete axis are located between labels or cross the labels.

subMembers.name: Font
subMembers.description: Font properties.

subMembers.name: color
subMembers.description: Specifies font color.

subMembers.name: family
subMembers.description: Specifies font family.

subMembers.name: opacity
subMembers.description: Specifies font opacity.

subMembers.name: size
subMembers.description: Specifies font size.

subMembers.name: weight
subMembers.description: Specifies font weight. Accepts values from 100 to 900 in increments of 100. Higher values increase boldness.

subMembers.name: GradientColor
subMembers.description: Specifies colors on which gradient is based.

subMembers.name: color
subMembers.description: Specifies one of the gradient colors.

subMembers.name: offset
subMembers.description: Specifies the starting point of a color.

properties.name: HatchDirection
properties.description: Specifies the direction of hatching lines.

properties.name: LabelOverlap
properties.description: Decides how to arrange scale/axis labels when there is not enough space to keep all of them.

properties.name: LabelPosition
properties.description: Specifies a label position relative to the chart.

properties.name: LegendHoverMode
properties.description: Specifies what series elements to highlight when a corresponding item in the legend is hovered over.

properties.name: LegendMarkerState
properties.description: The marker's state.

properties.name: Palette
properties.description: Sets the palette to be used for colorizing chart elements.

properties.name: PaletteColorSet
properties.description: Returns a subset of palette colors.

properties.name: PaletteExtensionMode
properties.description: Specifies how to extend the palette when it contains less colors than the number of chart points/series.

properties.name: PointInteractionMode
properties.description: Specifies series elements to be highlighted when a user interacts with a series point.

properties.name: PointSymbol
properties.description: Specifies which symbol should represent series points in scatter, line- and area-like series.

properties.name: RelativePosition
properties.description: Specifies the position of a chart element on the plot.

properties.name: ScaleBreakLineStyle
properties.description: Specifies the scale breaks' line style.

properties.name: SeriesHoverMode
properties.description: Specifies series elements to be highlighted when a user points to a series.

properties.name: SeriesSelectionMode
properties.description: Specifies series elements to be highlighted when a user selects a series.

properties.name: SeriesType
properties.description: Sets the series type.

properties.name: ShiftLabelOverlap
properties.description: Specifies how a chart should behave when point/bar/item labels overlap.

properties.name: TextOverflow
properties.description: Specifies how to arrange chart text elements that overflow their containers: hide, truncated them with ellipsis, or leave them as they are.

properties.name: Theme
properties.description: Sets the name of the theme the UI component uses.

properties.name: TimeInterval
properties.description: Specifies various time intervals.

properties.name: ValueErrorBarDisplayMode
properties.description: Specifies whether error bars must be displayed in full or partially.

properties.name: ValueErrorBarType
properties.description: Specifies how error bar values must be calculated.

properties.name: VisualRangeUpdateMode
properties.description: Specifies how the selected or visual range should behave when data is updated.

properties.name: WordWrap
properties.description: Specifies how to wrap texts that do not fit into a single line.

properties.name: ZoomPanAction
properties.description: Specifies zoom or pan mode.
